==Walsall F.C. youth team==
The youth team play in the [[Football League Youth Alliance|Youth Alliance North West Conference]]. These include [[Matty Fryatt]], [[Julian Bennett (footballer)|Julian Bennett]], [[Scott Dann]], [[Alex Nicholls (footballer)|Alex Nicholls]], [[Richard Taundry]], [[Troy Deeney]] and many more.  Before that the successful youth system also saw ex-England internationals [[Michael Ricketts]] and [[Allan Clarke (footballer)|Allan Clarke]] also progress through the ranks to go on and represent their country, with the later Allan Clarke also scoring a winning goal in an [[FA Cup]] final while at [[Leeds United A.F.C.|Leeds United]].

